{
  "texts": [
    "The LLaMA model emerged as a significant milestone, demonstrating an enhanced ability to understand context and generate coherent and contextually relevant text [23,24].",
    "Studies have shown that LLaMA's architecture, built upon deep learning principles, enables a level of linguistic understanding that surpasses its predecessors [25,26].",
    "However, research has also highlighted a gap in these models' ability to precisely tailor information retrieval to specific user queries, often leading to results that, while linguistically accurate, may lack relevance or specificity [2,20,27,21,28].",
    "This limitation has been a driving factor for exploring new approaches to optimize LLMs for targeted information retrieval tasks.",
    "Reinforcement Learning in AIReinforcement learning has emerged as a critical methodology in the field of artificial intelligence, especially in scenarios where decision-making is crucial [28,29,22,30,1,31,8]."
  ]
}